this week. Among the players reporting for work will be several Valley alums. . 
. . Ex-local players include: Mitchell Butler (Oakwood High), Lucious Harris 
and Trevor Wilson (Cleveland High), and Isaiah Rider Jr. (Antelope Valley 
College). 
