Within, a classical theater company beginning its third season. This fall's 
offerings include John Steinbeck's "Of Mice and Men" and Shakespeare's "King 
Lear." . . . The group also hopes to move to a mid-sized house, and will become 
a touring company under an Equity touring contract. See Valley Life! Page 3. 
Michael Arkush 
