</P>
<P>
 GOP: 14% 
</P>
<P>
 Ind./Other: 45% The Issues 
</P>
<P>
 Kennedy: Campaign is trying to paint Romney as a high-flying corporate 
speculator who's misleading voters about his record. 
</P>
<P>
 Romney: Argues Kennedy's 32 years in the Senate have left him out of touch on 
issues like spending, welfare and crime. The Candidates 
</P>
<P>
 Kennedy: Has spent almost his entire adult life in the Senate and ranks as one 
of its most influential, and liberal, members. 
</P>
<P>
 Romney: A venture capitalist and son of a former Michigan governor, is making 
his first run for public office. Kennedy's Senate Race Record 
