<P>
 Police are investigating a traffic accident in which an unidentified jogger 
was struck and critically injured Thursday night. 
</P>
<P>
 The victim, a woman, was hit just before 7:30 p.m. near Magnolia Street and 
Martin Avenue, Sgt. Keith Levin said.Several passersby, who had emergency 
medical training, provided assistance until the woman could be transported to 
UCI Medical Center in Orange with severe head injuries. 
</P>
