he and another store employee were confronted by two men, one armed with an ice 
pick and the other with a handgun, outside the store after closing. 
</P>
<P>
 The $50,000 reward for information leading to the conviction of the killers 
was posted by the Washington-based Price-Costco corporation, owners of the 
Price Club. Anyone with information on the crime can call Inglewood detectives 
at (310) 412-5246 or an anonymous 24-hour crime hot line at (310) 412-8825. 
